  </div>


<p>Удаление модуля:</p>








  <div class="shortcode shortcode-codeblock shortcode-codeblock-sh">
    <div class="d-flex mb-3 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="flex-grow-1 rounded overflow-hidden" id="clipboard-81bee479d4537c5864a9f5bcea9ba808"><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"><span class="line"><span class="cl">git submodule deinit -f <span class="o">[</span>MODULE<span class="o">]</span>  <span class="se">\
