<h2 id="изменение-адреса-репозитория">
    Изменение адреса репозитория
  <sup><a class="text-body-secondary small" href="#%d0%b8%d0%b7%d0%bc%d0%b5%d0%bd%d0%b5%d0%bd%d0%b8%d0%b5-%d0%b0%d0%b4%d1%80%d0%b5%d1%81%d0%b0-%d1%80%d0%b5%d0%bf%d0%be%d0%b7%d0%b8%d1%82%d0%be%d1%80%d0%b8%d1%8f"><i class="fas fa-link fa-fw"></i></a></sup>
</h2><p>Показать текущий адрес:</p>








  <div class="shortcode shortcode-codeblock shortcode-codeblock-sh">
    <div class="d-flex mb-3 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="flex-grow-1 rounded overflow-hidden" id="clipboard-8aa6b52a2ce71119736e790c7c0aadf6"><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"><span class="line"><span class="cl">git remote -v</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
